Hermes to Sell French-Made Saris in India for $8,200, FT Reports

-- B y   P a u l   D o b s o n
-- 
2011-10-08T09:35:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-08/hermes-to-sell-french-made-saris-in-india-for-8-200-ft-reports.html
Hermes International (RMS)  SCA plans to
sell French-made saris costing between $6,100 and $8,200 in its
Indian stores, the Financial Times said, citing an interview
with Chief Executive Officer  Patrick Thomas .  To contact the reporter on this story:
